what_worked: Applied prefetch_fact_join, single_pass_aggregation, multi_dimension_prefetch: Pre-filtered all dimension tables into separate CTEs before joining with store_sales, then used conditional aggregation to compute both promotional and total sales in a single pass through the fact table. This eliminates duplicate scans of store_sales and early reduces data volume.
why_it_worked: Pre-joining filtered dimensions with fact table before aggregation reduces join input; Consolidating repeated scans into CASE aggregates reduces I/O from N scans to 1; Pre-filtering multiple dimension tables in parallel reduces join fan-out
